	<string name="charwizard_header_instructions">INSTRUCTIONS</string>
	<string name="charwizard_message_instructions_class">Choose your Character Class.\r\r1. Review the available Class options by clicking on their links or names.\r2. Click the Add button next to the Class option you want.\r3. Review available Class Proficiencies and Features; and resolve any outstanding choices using drop-down selection boxes or Add buttons.\r4. If you want to make a character higher than level 1, either use the arrow keys next to Class level field to increase/decrease the Class level, or use Add Class button to create a multi-class Character.</string>
	<string name="charwizard_message_instructions_background">Choose your Character Background.\r\r1. Review the available Background options by clicking on their links or names.\r2. Click the Add button next to the Background option you want.\r3.Review available Background Proficiencies and Features; and resolve any outstanding choices using drop-down selection boxes or Add buttons.</string>
	<string name="charwizard_message_instructions_species">Choose your Character Species/Ancestry.\r\r1. Review the available Species and Ancestry options by clicking on their links or names.\r2. Click the Add button next to the Species option you want.\r3. If the Species has Ancestry options, then click the Add button next to the Ancestry option you want.\r4.Review available Species Proficiencies and Traits; and resolve any outstanding choices using drop-down selection boxes or Add buttons.</string>
	<string name="charwizard_message_instructions_abilities">Choose your Starting Ability method and details.\r\r1.Choose a Ability Score generation method by clicking on the Method drop-down selection box.\r2A. For Dice Roll / Manual Entry, either click the roll button to make an automatic 3d6 dice roll for ability scores, or enter the Base scores manually.\r2B. For Point Buy, click on the up/down buttons in the Base section to spend the points noted in the Abilities header.\r2C. For Standard Array, click and drag the Base scores between each other to swap values.</string>
	<string name="charwizard_message_instructions_equipment">Choose your Equipment Starting Kit and Currency choices\r\r1. Once your Class and Background are selected, choose from the available Starting Kit options for both Class and Background to set your Starting Equipment and Currency.\r2.If you are making D&amp;D (Legacy) character, you can make a Starting Wealth roll instead of selecting Starting Kits.</string>
	<string name="charwizard_message_instructions_commit">To complete your character, take the following steps.\r\r1. Review warnings (if any) and return to previous sections to resolve.\r2. Enter your character name.\r3. Review character to make sure everything looks right.\r4. Click the Save button to finalize and create Character record.</string>
	<string name="charwizard_message_instructions_class_levelup">Choose the Character Class that you want to Level Up.\r\r1. Click the Level Up button to level up one of your existing classes; or click the Add Class button to add a new class.</string>
	<string name="charwizard_message_instructions_commit_levelup">To complete your Character level up, take the following steps.\r\r1. Review warnings and return to previous sections to resolve.\r2. Review character to make sure everything looks right.\r3. Click the Save button to finalize Character Level Up changes.</string>

